                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18131201-48-off265 t18131201-48-cd266"></join>, four silver table-spoons, value 2 l. a silver dessert-spoon, value 7 s. three silver tea-spoons, value 6 s. a silver salt-spoon, value 1 s. 8 d. a gold chain, value 10 s. a silver<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181312010048"></xptr>snuff-box, value 12 s. and a gold broach, value 1 l.
